.%20Kennedy%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Trump%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bbaby%20blue%20doesn't%20fit%20with%20us%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20wanted%20a%20dark%20blue%2C%20white%2C%20and%20red%20plane.%20The%20design%20was%20rejected%20after%20a%20thermal%20study%20found%20the%20dark%20blue%20color%20could%20emit%20additional%20heat%20and%20would%20need%20more%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdf68225-b7c6-418c-a688-baa2f9aff582%5C%22%3EA%20difficult%20time%20for%20Boeing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20Trump%20and%20Boeing%20signed%20in%202018%20is%20a%20fixed-price%20agreement%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20planemaker%20responsible%20for%20any%20cost%20overruns.%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-lost-money-over-trump-demands-for-air-force-one-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enegotiated%20the%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20threatened%20to%20cancel%20the%20contract%20if%20it%20went%20above%20%243.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeings-losses-air-force-one-project-two-billion-donald-trump-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelays%20have%20cost%20Boeing%20over%20%242%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20raised%20total%20project%20costs%20to%20around%20%245.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20then-CEO%20David%20Calhoun%20called%20the%20Air%20Force%20One%20project%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unique%20set%20of%20risks%20that%20Boeing%20probably%20shouldn't%20have%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20challenges%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%2033%2C000%20Boeing%20workers%20went%20on%20strike.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-workers-approve-labor-contract-end-strike-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalkout%20lasted%20nearly%20two%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20left%20Boeing%20with%20a%20backlog%20of%20a