nt%20Shinde%2C%20Shambhavi%20Chaudhary%2C%20Rajkumar%20Sangwan%2C%20Jiten%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20Anupriya%20Patel%20and%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20Singh%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20speak%20during%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20leaders%20of%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20likely%20to%20refer%20to%20Emergency%20and%20speak%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bfake%20narratives%20being%20peddled%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20leaders%20TR%20Balu%20and%20A%20Raja%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MPs%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20and%20Mohua%20Moitra%20are%20likely%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Congress%20party%20have%20issued%20a%20'three%20line%20whip'%20to%20ensure%20the%20presence%20of%20their%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20BJP%20members%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20are%20hereby%20informed%20that%20the%2075th%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%2013th%20of%20December%20and%20Saturday%2C%20the%2014th%20of%20December%202024.%20All%20members%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20are%2C%20therefore%2C%20requested%20to%20be%20positively%20present%20in%20the%20House%20throughout%20both%20days%20i.e.%20Friday%2C%20the%2013th%20of%20December%20and%20Saturday%2C%20the%201of%204th%20of%20December%202024%20and%20support%20the%20Government's%20stand%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20statement%20of%20the%20BJP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20will%20initiate%20the%20debate%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20December%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20wants%20the%20House%20to%20run%20and%20have%20a%20debate%20on%2075%20years%20of%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20on%20December%2013-14.%3C%2