0Musk%20has%20slammed%20the%20US%20market%20regulator%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20(SEC)%20over%20probes%20into%20Neuralink%20-%20a%20neurotechnology%20firm%20owned%20by%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%20-%20and%20the%20purchase%20of%20Twitter%20shares.%20His%20lawyer%20Alex%20Spiro%20has%20flagged%20over%20%26quot%3Bsix%20years%20of%20harassment%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Commission%20and%20its%20staff%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20from%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20SEC%2C%20Gary%20Clenser%2C%20who%20had%20directed%20these%20actions%20-%20him%20or%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20tactics%20and%20misguided%20scheme%20will%20not%20intimidate%20us.%20We%20reserve%20all%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20letter%20sent%20via%20Musk's%20lawyer%20to%20Clenser%2C%20who%20has%20already%20been%20facing%20Team%20Trump's%20wrath%20over%20his%20anti-crypto%20wrath.%20Sharing%20the%20letter%20on%20X%2C%20Musk%20said%20sarcastically%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20Gary%2C%20how%20could%20you%20do%20this%20to%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20said%20Musk%20had%20been%20served%20a%20settlement%20demand%20by%20the%20SEC%20staff%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20accept%20a%20monetary%20payment%20or%20face%20charges%20on%20numerous%20counts.%20It%20said%20the%20demand%20followed%20a%20directive%20from%20their%20superiors%20and%20that%20the%20charges%20would%20be%20brought%20imminently%20unless%20Musk%20accepted%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20mention%20what%20the%20charges%20may%20be%20and%20how%20they%20may%20impact%20companies%20owned%20by%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20the%20SEC%20recently%20summoned%20him%20to%20record%20his%20testimony%20and%20threatened%20him%20with%20a%20process%20server%20if%20he%20did%20not%20cooperate.%20He%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bcategorically%20refused%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20a%20probe%20was%20opened%20into%20Neuralink%2C%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20series%20of%20events%20makes%20(it)%20clear%20that%20the%20Commission%20is%20not%20motivated%20to%20seek%20the%20truth%20but%20instead%20is%20engaged%20in%20an%20improperly%20motivated%20campaign%20against%20Mr%20Musk%20and%20the%20individuals%20associated%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClenser%20will%20step%20down%20as%20the%20SEC%20chief%20on%20January%2020%20with%20Donald%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20Trump%20had%20earlier%20said%20he%20would%20fire%20Clenser%20on%20his%20first%20day%20as%20President%20and%20end%20his%20administration's%20%26quot%3Banti-crypto%20crusade%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20earlier%20said%20he%20does%20not%20respect%20the%20SEC%2C%20has%20had%20a%20long%20history%20with%20the%20market%20regulator.%20In%202018%2C%20after%20Musk%20said%20he%20would%20take%20Tesla%20private%20but%20then%20admitted%20it%20would%20remain%20public%2C%20the%20SEC%20sued%20him%20over%20an%20online%20post%20stating%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bfunding%20secured%26quot%3B%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20ownership%20move.%20Musk%20had%20paid%20%2420%20million%20to%20settle%20the%20case%20with%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20stepped%20down%20as%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Tesla%20board%20and%20agreed%20to%20have%20a%20lawyer%20supervise%20his%20posts%20on%20Twitter%20-%20a%20microblogging%20site%20that%20was%20later%20bought%20by%20him%20and%20went%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734067380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Firdt2pa_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_27_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthese-tactics-elon-musk-slams-us-markets-regulator-over-neuralink-probe-7237196%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20slammed%20the%20US%20market%20regulator%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20(SEC)%20over