ime-in-a-month-7237209%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20received%20a%20bomb%20threat%20via%20email%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20such%20incident%20in%20a%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-gets-bomb-threat-in-russian-language-2nd-time-in-a-month-7237209%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Indians%20Shine%20On%20Forbes'%202024%20World's%20Most%20Powerful%20Women%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EForbes%20has%20unveiled%20its%2021st%20annual%20list%20of%20The%20World's%20100%20Most%20Powerful%20Women%2C%20a%20ranking%20of%20influential%20figures%20from%20industries%20such%20as%20business%2C%20entertainment%2C%20politics%2C%20philanthropy%20and%20policymaking.%20Among%20these%20global%20changemakers%20are%20three%20Indian%20women%20who%20have%20made%20remarkable%20strides%20in%20their%20respective%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20their%20profiles%20and%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman%20(%2328)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%2028%20on%20the%20list%20is%20Minister%20of%20Finance%20and%20Corporate%20Affairs%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman.%20In%20May%202019%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20hold%20these%20roles%20full-time.%20She%20was%20reappointed%20after%20the%20general%20elections%20in%20June%202024.%20Tasked%20with%20managing%20India's%20nearly%20%244%20trillion%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fifth%20largest%20globally%20%E2%80%94%20Sitharaman%20projects%20that%20the%20nation's%20GDP%20will%20soon%20surpass%20Japan%20and%20Germany%2C%20positioning%20India%20as%20the%20third-largest%20economy%20by%202027.%20An%20advocate%20for%20women's%20financial%20empowerment%2C%20she%20has%20championed%20initiatives%20supporting%20entrepreneurship%2C%20access%20to%20credit%20and%20financial%20literacy%20among%20women.%20Before%20entering%20politics%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20held%20positions%20at%20the%20Agricultural%20Engineers%20Association%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20BBC%20World%20Service.%20She%20also%20served%20as%20a%20member%20of%20India's%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoshni%20Nadar%20Malhotra%20(%2381)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanked%2081st%20on%20the%20list%2C%20Roshni%20Nadar%20Malhotra%20is%20the%20Chairperson%20of%20HCL%20Technologies%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20leading%20IT%20services%20firms%2C%20and%20CEO%20of%20HCL%20Corporation.%20She%20oversees%20strategic%20decisions%20for%20the%20%2412%20billion%20enterprise%20founded%20by%20her%20father%2C%20Shiv%20Nadar%2C%20in%201976.%20Apart%20from%20her%20corporate%20achievements%2C%20Ms%20Malhotra%20is%20a%20trustee%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Nadar%20Foundation%2C%20focusing%20on%20transformative%20education%20and%20establishing%20some%20of%20India's%20premier%20institutions.%20She%20also%20founded%20The%20Habitats%20Trust%2C%20an%20initiative%20dedicated%20to%20conserving%20natural%20habitats%20and%20indigenous%20species.%20She%20has%20a%20background%20in%20journalism%20and%20holds%20an%20MBA%20from%20the%20Kellogg%20School%20of%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20(%2382)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanked%2082nd%20in%20Forbes'%20Power%20Women%20list%20and%2091st%20among%20India's%20richest%20individuals%20in%202024%2C%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20has%20earned%20her%20place%20as%20a%20trailblazer%20in%20biotechnology.%20She%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Biocon%2C%20a%20biopharmaceutical%20company%20she%20established%20in%201978.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20Biocon%20has%20expanded%20into%20international%20markets%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20and%20operates%20one%20of%20Asia's%20largest%20insulin%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20Malaysia.%20Mazumdar-Shaw's%20accomplishments%20include%20Biocon%20Biologics'%20acquisition%20of%20Viatris'%20biosimilars%20business%20for%20%243.3%20billion%20in%202022%20and%20the%20IPO%20of%20Biocon-backed%20Bicara%20Therapeutics%2C%20which%20raised%20%24362%20million%20on%20Nasdaq%20in%20September%202024.%20Despite%20her%20initial%20aspiration%20to%20become%20a%20doctor%2C%20Ms%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20pursued%20a%20different%20path%20and%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20successful%20entrepreneurs.%20In%202019%2C%20she%20and%20her%20late%20husband%2C%20John%20Shaw%2C%20donated%20%247.5%20million%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Glasgow%20to%20advance%20cancer%20research.%20Her%20company%20is%20also%20collaborating%20on%20antibody%20therapy%20for%20coronavirus%20variants.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734064080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fgn4rrcm8_nirmala-sitharaman-roshni-nadar-malhotra-and-kiran-mazumdarshaw-forbes_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforbes-2024-worlds-most-powerful-women-list-3-indians-shine-on-forbes-2024-worlds-most-powerful-women-list-7237150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Forbes%20has%20unveiled%20its%2021st%20annual%20list%20of%20The%20World's%20100%20Most%20Powerful%20Women%2C%20a%20ranking%20of%20influential%20figures%20from%20industries%20such%20as%20business%2C%20entertainment%2C%20politics%2C%20philanthropy%20and%20policymaking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforbes-2024-worlds-most-powerful-women-list-3-indians-shine-on-forbes-2024-worlds-most-powerful-women-list-7237150%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSuspicious%2C%20Requires%20Investigation%26quot%3B%3A%20Big%20Accusation%20On%20Gukesh's%20Title%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDefending%20world%20chess%20champion%20Ding%20Liren%20was%20made%20to%20rue%20the%20'blunder'%20he%20made%20in%20the%2014th%20and%20final%20game%20against%20India's%20D%20Gukesh%20on%20Thursday.%20Liren's%20error%20of%20judgment%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20costly%20one%20as%20Gukesh%20pounced%20on%20the%20mistake%20to%20become%20the%20youngest%20world%20champion%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20game.%20While%20most%20of%20the%20chess%20fraternity%20is%20elated%20to%20see%20the%2018-year-old%20Gukesh%20make%20history%2C%20Russian%20Chess%20Federation%20chief%20Andrei%20Filatov%20has%20accused%20China's%20Liren%20of%20losing%20the%20game%20on%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20news%20agency%20TASS%20quoted%20Filatov%20asking%20the%20International%20Chess%20Federation%20(FIDE)%20to%20open%20a%20probe%20and%20investigate%20the%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20result%20of%20the%20last%20game%20caused%20bewilderment%20among%20professionals%20and%20chess%20fans.%20The%20actions%20of%20the%20Chinese%20chess%20player%20in%20the%20decisive%20segment%20are%20extremely%20suspicious%20and%20require%20a%20separate%20investigation%20by%20FIDE%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLosing%20the%20position%20in%20which%20Ding%20Liren%20was%20is%20difficult%20even%20for%20a%20first-class%20player.%20The%20defeat%20of%20the%20Chinese%20chess%20player%20in%20today's%20game%20raises%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20and%20looks%20like%20a%20deliberate%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20emotional%20moment%20that%2018-year-old%20Gukesh%20Dommaraju%20became%20the%2018th%20world%20chess%20champion%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjRIZrYeyCF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjRIZrYeyCF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Chess.com%20(%40chesscom)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchesscom%2Fstatus%2F1867195384969216129%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20forward%20the%20incredible%20legacy%20of%20the%20great%20Viswanathan%20Anand%2C%20Gukesh%20became%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20to%20clinch%20the%20coveted%20prize%20after%20the%20iconic%20player%2C%20who%20owned%20the%20crown%20five%20times%20in%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20settling%20into%20%26quot%3Bsemi-retirement%26quot%3B%2C%20the%2055-year-old%20Anand%2C%20incidentally%2C%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20shaping%20Gukesh%20at%20his%20chess%20academy%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGukesh%20secured%20the%20requisite%207.5%20points%20as%20against%206.5%20of%20his%20Chinese%20rival%20after%20winning%20the%2014th%20and%20last%20classical%20time%20control%20game%20of%20the%20match%20that%20seemed%20headed%20for%20a%20draw%20for%20most%20part.%20As%20winner%2C%20he%20will%20walk%20away%20with%20a%20whopping%20USD%201.3%20million%20(approx%20Rs%2011.03%20crore)%20from%20the%202.5%20million%20prize%20purse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20dreaming%20this%20moment%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20I%20realised%20the%20dream%20(and%20made%20it)%20into%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20soft-spoken%20Chennai-lad%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20historic%20triumph%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reticent%20teenager%20grinned%20widely%20and%20raised%20his%20arms%20in%20celebration%20after%20the%20victory%2C%20a%20stark%20contrast%20from%20the%20poker%20face%20he%20usually%20sports%20while%20playing.%20Once%20the%20feeling%20settled%20in%2C%20a%20tear%20or%20two%20also%20escaped%20his%20eyes%2C%20showing%20a%20rare%20moment%20of%20vulnerability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20bit%20emotional%20because%20I%20was%20not%20expecting%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734063900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F525r2t1_ding-liren-and-d-gu