s.%20The%20film%20had%20an%20exceptional%20opening%20with%20Rs%20164.25%20crore%2C%20and%20its%20opening%20weekend%20saw%20an%20impressive%20Rs%20529%20crore%20nett%2C%20breaking%20multiple%20records.%20However%2C%20collections%20began%20to%20dip%20over%20the%20weekdays%2C%20with%20Rs%2064.45%20crore%20on%20Monday%2C%20Rs%2051.55%20crore%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20Rs%2042%20crore%20on%20Wednesday.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20the%20film%20earned%20Rs.%2025.59%20crore%20domestically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20film's%20impressive%20earnings%2C%20the%20occupancy%20in%20theatres%20has%20been%20declining.%20In%20the%20Telugu%20market%2C%20the%20movie%20has%20seen%20an%20overall%20occupancy%20rate%20of%2024.63%25%2C%20with%20morning%20shows%20at%2014.41%25%2C%20afternoon%20shows%20at%2023.85%25%2C%20evening%20shows%20and%20night%20shows%20at%2030.56%25%20and%2029.68%25%20respectively.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Hindi%20market%20showed%20an%20overall%20occupancy%20of%2028.93%25%2C%20with%20morning%20and%20afternoon%20shows%20at%2012.72%25%20and%2024.70%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20according%20to%20Sacnilk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20just%20seven%20days%20of%20its%20release%2C%20the%20film%20has%20crossed%20the%20remarkable%20milestone%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20worldwide%2C%20making%20it%20the%20highest-grossing%20Indian%20film%20of%202024.%20Having%20surpassed%20Prabhas'%20%3Cem%3EKalki%202898%20AD%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20earned%20Rs%201%2C042.25%20crore%20in%20its%20lifetime%20collection%2C%20%3Cem%3EPushpa%202%20%3C%2Fem%3Enow%20sets%20its%20sights%20on%20beating%20other%20massive%20blockbusters%20of%20all%20time%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EBaahubali%202%3A%20The%20Conclusion%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rs%201%2C788.06%20crore)%2C%20RRR%20(Rs%201%2C230%20crore)%2C%20%3Cem%3EKGF%3A%20Chapter%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rs%201%2C215%20crore)%2C%20%3Cem%3EJawan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Rs%201%2C160%20crore)%20and%20%3Cem%3EDangal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2016)%2C%20which%20grossed%20Rs%202%2C070.3%20crore%20globally%2C%20to%20secure%20the%20title%20of%20the%20all-time%20highest-grossing%20Indian%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirected%20by%20Sukumar%2C%20%3Cem%3EPushpa%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20picks%20up%20where%20its%20predecessor%2C%20Pushpa%3A%20The%20Rise%20(2021)%2C%20left%20off.%20The%20much-anticipated%20sequel%20continues%20the%20story%20of%20red%20sandalwood%20smuggling%2C%20with%20Allu%20Arjun%20reprising%20his%20role%20as%20Pushpa%20Raj%2C%20alongside%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%20as%20Srivalli%20and%20Fahadh%20Faasil%20as%20Bhanwar%20Singh%20Shekawat.%20The%20film%20also%20features%20seasoned%20actors%20such%20as%20Jagapathi%20Babu%2C%20Dhananjaya%2C%20Rao%20Ramesh%2C%20Sunil%20and%20Anasuya%20Bharadwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734062280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fg64aftq8_s_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpushpa-2-box-office-collection-day-8-allu-arjun-and-rashmika-mandannas-film-beats-kalki-2898-ad-becomes-highest-grossing-indian-movie-of-2024-7237096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prabhas'%20Kalki%202898%20AD%20earned%20Rs%201%2C042.25%20crore%20in%20its%20lifetime%20collection%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpushpa-2-box-office-collection-day-8-allu-arjun-and-rashmika-mandannas-film-beats-kalki-2898-ad-becomes-highest-grossing-indian-movie-of-2024-7237096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Okami%E2%80%99%20Sequel%20Video%20Game%20in%20the%20Works%20From%20Hideki%20Kamiya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734061840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FOkami.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236248127%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20sequel%20to%20the%20beloved%20game%20%E2%80%9COkami%E2%80%9D%20is%20in%20the%20works%20at%20Cap