od%20comes%20back.%20He's%20had%20no%20hiccups%2C%20he%20had%20a%20really%20good%20bowl%20yesterday%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20previous%2C%26quot%3B%20skipper%20Cummins%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BHim%20and%20the%20medical%20team%20are%20super%20confident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20other%20changes%20for%20the%20Test%20starting%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECummins%20admitted%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20leave%20out%20Boland%2C%20but%20suggested%20he%20could%20still%20play%20a%20part%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tough%2C%20he%20was%20fantastic%20in%20Adelaide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%2035-year-old%20seamer%2C%20who%20bagged%20five%20wickets%20in%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20unfortunately%20spent%20a%20fair%20bit%20of%20time%20on%20the%20bench%20over%20the%20past%2018%20months.%20And%20whenever%20he's%20played%2C%20he's%20been%20fantastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20shame%20for%20Scotty%2C%20but%20still%20a%20fair%20bit%20to%20play%20out%20this%20series.%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20he%20doesn't%20get%20another%20crack%20at%20some%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gabba%20used%20to%20be%20a%20fortress%20for%20Australia%2C%20who%20were%20unbeaten%20there%20since%201988%20until%20India%20finally%20breached%20it%20in%202021%20to%20clinch%20their%20four-Test%20series%202-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20won%20their%20next%20two%20Tests%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20against%20England%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20but%20were%20upset%20again%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20the%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECummins%20played%20down%20the%20significance%20of%20results%20at%20particular%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20venue%20really.%20We%20play%20at%20dozens%20and%20dozens%20of%20venues%20each%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20good%20coming%20back%20to%20a%20place%20that%20is%20familiar.%20A