C%20determined%20to%20find%20solutions%20along%20the%20way.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20blessed%20by%20the%20Almighty%20with%20the%20courage%20to%20pursue%20a%20successful%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20took%20over%20the%20spotlight%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20an%20intense%20experience%20for%20everyone%20involved.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20crew%20worked%20tirelessly%2C%20often%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20to%20make%20this%20film%20what%20it%20is%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Indira.%20Looking%20back%2C%20she%20feels%20the%20struggles%20shaped%20her%20in%20ways%20she%E2%80%99ll%20always%20cherish.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20road%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20but%20the%20depth%20of%20self-made%20success%20is%20something%20I%E2%80%99ll%20always%20carry%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndira%20and%20her%20team%20screened%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20prestigious%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMarch%C3%A9%20du%20Film%20%3C%2Fem%3E(or%20Cannes%20Film%20Market).%20Though%20the%20film%20was%20screened%20out%20of%20competition%2C%20the%20response%20was%20moving.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20emotionally%20overwhelmed%20and%20cried%20when%20I%20turned%20back%20to%20see%20the%20audience%20appreciating%20the%20film.%20Many%20international%20filmmakers%20and%20scriptwriters%20approached%20me%20to%20discuss%20it%2C%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Indira.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indira%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C