0going%20to%20see%20arrangements%20that%20look%20more%20like%20NFL%20programs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261128ddb-3d1b-44d4-8d8a-3fd479aad9db%5C%22%3EBelichick's%20move%20is%20part%20of%20a%20bigger%20trend%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBelichick's%20hire%20isn't%20the%20only%20signal%20that%20managing%20a%20college%20sports%20team%20is%20looking%20a%20lot%20more%20like%20managing%20a%20pro%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20longtime%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0d836ca8cdfccb54e74d1d01162de6e1df6f7c5ca0ecc73e5157bc08666e13a8%26postID%3D675b163fda9529753711bf75%26postSlug%3Dbill-belichick-unc-coach-college-football-more-like-nfl-nil-2024-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Fnba%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F41313868%252Fadrian-wojnarowski-retires-espn-joins-st-bonaventure%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPN%20reporter%20Adrian%20Wojnarowski%3C%2Fa%3E%20left%20the%20outlet%20to%20become%20general%20manager%20of%20the%20men's%20basketball%20program%20at%20St.%20Bonaventure%20University%20%E2%80%94%20where%20he%20went%20to%20school%20%E2%80%94%20to%20work%20on%20NIL%20deals%20and%20recruiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Belichick%20will%20be%20getting%20some%20help%20at%20UNC%20from%20Michael%20Lombardi%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sports%20host%20and%20former%20NFL%20exec%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvsin.com%2Fcollege-football%2Fvsin-host-michael-lombardi-leaving-to-join-bill-belichick-at-university-of-north-carolina%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20Wednesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20night%20that%20he'll%20serve%20as%20the%20general%20manager%20of%20the%20Tar%20Heels%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Belichick%2C%20there%20are%20family%20ties%20to%20UNC.%20His%20father%20was%20an%20assistant%20football%20coach%20for%20the%20Tar%20Heels%20in%20the%20'50s.%20And%20The%20Guardian's%20Ollie%20Connolly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FOllieConnolly%2Fstatus%2F1865122110189760587%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1865122110189760587%257Ctwgr%255E306285f22dbf2fd620ca04c951b800d5e0035948%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fkeepingitheel.com%252Fthere-s-a-major-rumored-guarantee-in-the-bill-belichick-unc-football-discussions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eciting%20anonymous%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reported%20last%20week%20that%20as%20part%20of%20his%20deal%2C%20Belichick%20sought%20a%20guarantee%20that%20his%20son%20would%20succeed%20him%20as%20head%20coach%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20reported%20that%20UNC%20is%20open%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Rishe%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Sports%20Business%20Program%20at%20Washington%20University%20in%20St.%20Louis%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Belichick's%20move%20doesn't%20necessarily%20portend%20an%20exodus%20of%20NFL%20coaches%20to%20college%20towns%20because%20Belichick's%20situation%20was%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20Alabama%20or%20Ohio%20State%20are%20going%20to%20be%20recruiting%20Andy%20Reid%20away%20from%20the%20Chiefs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Kansas%20City's%20head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Rishe%20said%2C%20his%20move%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20coaches%20are%20free%20agents%20just%20as%20players%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERishe%20said%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20forces%20animating%20college%20football's%20bulk-up%20is%20money%20flowing%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnil-year-two-takeaways-college-sports-collectives-student-athletes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENIL%20collectives%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20collective%20money%2C%20already%20used%20to%20recruit%20players%2C%20could%20also%20be%20directed%20toward%20bringing%20on%20coaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collectives%20gather%20money%20from%20donors%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20players.%20For%20example%2C%20at%20Fuess's%20University%20of%20Nebraska%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.1890nebraska.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1890%20Initiative%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20its%20resident%2C%20independent%20NIL%20collective%20%E2%80%94%20raises%20money%20for%20athletes%20in%20exchange%20for%20donor%20perks%20like%20merch%20and%20invites%20to%20membership%20events.%20Its%20website%20says%20it%20partners%20with%20athletes%20%26quot%3Bto%20help%20them%20build%20personal%20brands%20through%20athletic%20endorsements%2C%20brand%20partnerships%2C%20and%20NIL%20compliance%20protocols.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ab08114-53b7-44a1-b840-beaaba82231d%5C%22%3EAn%20expanded%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFuess%20said%20that%20until%20recently%2C%20college%20athletes%20were%20limited%20in%20transferring%20to%20other%20programs.%20Now%2C%20that's%20no%20longer%20true%20because%20of%20the%20transfer%20portal%20window%2C%20which%20in%20October%20was%20reduced%20for%20Division%20I%20football%20and%20basketball%20players%20to%2030%20days.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20college%20coaches%20must%20work%20harder%20than%20ever%20to%20keep%20players%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20free%20agency%20is%20freer%20than%20in%20professional%20sports%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20college%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuess%2C%20who%20also%20serves%20as%20his%20campus's%20faculty%20representative%20to%20its%20athletic%20department%2C%20said%20college%20coaches%20increasingly%20have%20to%20know%20how%20to%20spot%20talent%2C%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-college-athletes-are-getting-paid-from-nil-endorsement-deals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20for%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20how%20to%20keep%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20there%20could%20be%20more%20people%20who%20come%20from%20the%20NFL%2C%20though%20they%20could%20also%20come%20from%20elsewhere%20in%20college%20athletics%2C%20he%20s