ion-agriculture-volunteer-work-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efunds%20to%20build%20dams%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20the%20village%20overcame%20its%20water%20scarcity%20issues%2C%20and%20even%20began%20supplying%20water%20to%20neighbouring%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBapu%20Kambale%20from%20Pingali-Kd%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20mechanic%2C%20and%20I%20know%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20Art%20of%20Living%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Water%20conservation%20has%20always%20been%20close%20to%20my%20heart%2C%20as%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20the%20devastating%20effects%20of%20drought.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20we%20had%20to%20walk%20up%20to%20seven%20kilometres%20just%20to%20fetch%20water.%20Our%20wells%20were%20dry%2C%20and%20finding%20drinking%20water%20was%20a%20constant%20struggle.%20With%20such%20a%20shortage%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20think%20of%20farming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20began%20his%20work%20on%20water%20conservation%20in%20our%20village%2C%20I%20joined%20him.%20We%20built%20dams%2C%20and%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20took%20the%20lead%20in%20raising%20funds.%20He%20stayed%20in%20our%20village%20for%20nearly%2040%20days%2C%20overseeing%20the%20progress%20and%20ensuring%20everything%20was%20done%20properly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20deep%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20boy%20diagnosed%20with%20polio%20to%20a%20man%20leading%20a%20movement%20for%20water%20conservation%20across%20villages%2C%20Abhay%20Todkar%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20a%20source%20of%20hope%20for%20others%20facing%20similar%20challenges.%20His%20story%20proves%20that%20no%20limitation%20can%20hold%20back%20the%20human%20spirit%20when%20fuelled%20by%20grit%20and%20a%20passion%20for%20serving%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Abhay%20Todkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3