9-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386908%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIta%20Fort%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20boasts%20a%20facade%20of%20brickwork%2016%2C200%20cubic%20metres%20in%20length%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tourmyindia.com%2Fstates%2Farunachalpradesh%2Fita-fort.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETour%20My%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20credit%20the%20ingenious%20structure%20to%20King%20Ramachandra%2C%20the%20last%20king%20of%20the%20Jitari%20dynasty%20that%20ruled%20in%20the%2011th%20century.%20However%2C%20Lila%20Gogoi%2C%20an%20authority%20on%20the%20Buranjis%20(a%20class%20of%20historical%20chronicles%20and%20manuscripts%20written%20initially%20in%20the%20Ahom)%20of%20Assam%2C%20reveals%20that%20Ita%20Fort%20was%20built%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Ahom%20King%20Chakradhwaj%20Simha%20in%201688%20AD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20spot%20on%20which%20the%20majestic%20fort%20once%20stood%20is%20marked%20by%20ruins.%20But%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20that%20deter%20you%20from%20making%20a%20trip%20here.%20There%20are%20always%20gorgeous%20views%20of%20Dikrang%20Valley%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Rabdentse%20Fort%2C%20Sikkim%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERabdentse%20was%20the%20second%20capital%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291858%2Fbest-ecofriendly-hostel-in-sikkim-started-by-sharma-sisters-sustainable-homestay-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKingdom%20of%20Sikkim%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%201670%20to%201814.%20The%20reason%20it%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98India%E2%80%99s%20very%20own%20Machu%20Pichu%E2%80%99%20is%20because%20its%20morphology%20bears%20an%20uncanny%20resemb