nic%20products%20to%20customers%20in%20the%20local%20community.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20it%20was%20just%20me%20sourcing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295019%2Fkarnataka-couple-runs-ngo-anisha-help-farmers-switch-to-organic-farmer-in-drought-prone-district%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducts%20from%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20delivering%20them%2C%20and%20figuring%20everything%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Manikanta.%20They%20began%20by%20offering%20a%20small%20selection%20of%20organic%20items%2C%20such%20as%20mangoes%2C%20millet%20flour%2C%20%3Cem%3Etoor%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20health%20mix%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20stable%20market%20for%20organic%20produce%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20building%20a%20steady%20supply%20chain%20proved%20to%20be%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20challenges.%20At%20first%2C%20many%20farmers%20were%20hesitant%20to%20sell%20their%20produce%20through%20Sreshte.%20They%20were%20used%20to%20selling%20in%20conventional%20markets%2C%20where%20they%20received%20lower%20prices%20and%20faced%20greater%20uncertainty.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20by%20working%20together%2C%20they%20could%20get%20fair%20prices%20and%20a%20stable%20market%20for%20their%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20about%20building%20trust.%E2%80%9D%20Despite%20the%20challenges%2C%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20persistence%20paid%20off%20when%20they%20opened%20their%20first%20official%20store%20in%20Guntur%20in%202019.%20By%20then%2C%20they%20had%20already%20started%20building%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20through%20personalised%20service%20and%20commitment%20to%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20model%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236549%2Fbihar-farmer-earns-lakhs-superfood-makhana-entrepreneur-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-cultivation-farming-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommitment%20to%20empowering%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20working%20with%20local%20farmers%20already%20practising%20organic%20farming%2C%20they%20introduced%20a%20buyback%20model%2C%20ensuring%20that%20farmers%20could%20sell%20their%20produce%20at%20premium%20prices%2C%20far%20above%20what%20they%20would%20receive%20in%20conventional%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20partnering%20with%20Sreshte%2C%20I%20struggled%20to%20sell%20my%20organic%20mangoes%20at%20fair%20prices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Maha%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Agiripalli%2C%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Krishna%20district.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20doubling%20my%20earnings%20and%20more%20committed%20to%20organic%20farming.%20I%20would%20earn%20just%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20my%20organic%20produce%20in%20the%20conventional%20market.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%204%20lakh%20in%20just%20one%20season.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maha%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Agiripalli%2C%20doubled%20his%20income%20by%20selling%20organic%20mangoes%20through%20Sreshte%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIM